        <p>Wazishare Solutions Company Limited is a company incorporated in Kenya registered as per the company’s act of Kenya and is mandated to undertake a variety of businesses including provision of ICT related services. Currently, the company is implementing mobile payment applications in the health sector aimed at supporting the low income bracket make health insurance contribution in the most convenient and affordable manner possible. This is made possible through a top notch system that enable users use mobile phone airtime to make monthly contributions. The system accumulates airtime on daily basis until it is enough to cater for the set minimum of ksh.500 as required by the National Health Insurance provider (NHIF)</p>
